pfler potatoes (small), cut into halves","24 large raw prawn cutlets, de-veined, with tails intact","salt, to season","1 tbsp sherry vinegar","1 ½ tbsp extra virgin olive oil","40 g eschalots, cut into fine dice"]},{"title":"Sweet pickled cucumbers","content":["150 g fresh Lebanese cucumbers (approx. 3), peeled, deseeded and cut into fine dice","50 g raw sugar","50 g white wine vinegar","100 g water"]},{"title":"Horseradish cream","content":["80 g thickened cream","50 g horseradish (see Tips)","60 g crème fraîche","½ tsp ground white pepper","salt, to taste"]},{"title":"Assembly","content":["1 tbsp pink peppercorns (optional)","½ bunch baby radishes, cut into quarters","5 sprigs fresh chervil","50 g salmon caviar (optional)"]}],"id":"r119889","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-2KEBk40Aigo\/XZMuHQF01UI\/AAAAAAAAaBY\/bq9IKaZjwugpRxwWDe-PazNH0FngG9dLgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_A8AcHqs0aJvDizvr.png","title":"Prawn salad with horseradish cream","publishedAt":"2017-01-22T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"7.8 g","fat":"8.8 g","uom":"per 1 portions","carbohydrates":"15.6 g","calories":"746 kJ \/ 177 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large plate, large bowl, bowl, plastic wrap, small bowl, serving platter, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["This recipe uses jarred horseradish. You can use fresh horseradish if you prefer. Simply place 50 g fresh horseradish into mixing bowl and grate <strong>5 sec\/speed 7. <\/strong>Scrape down sides of mixing bowl and grate <strong>4 sec\/speed 7. <\/strong>Use horseradish as per recipe.","Leftover horseradish cream is delicious with rare roast beef, cold meat and roast potatoes."],"basicInfo":["easy","45m","1h","8 portions"]}